{"tid":847600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【油塘劏房】海傲灣開放式179呎 細絕油塘","createTime":"2018-10-04T09:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T15:33:31.000Z","uid":206224,"like":1,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"7c88e7eeb09ed900231dabd113b7c75ed32d8f52","tid":847600,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181002/large/1538487078_6438.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181002%2Flarge%2F1538487078_6438.png&h=d52d9f1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n油塘區最細新盤誕生，九建（034）旗下油塘新盤海傲灣剛剛上樓書，樓書顯示，項目位於鯉魚門徑1號，大廈共2座，第1座分1A座及1B座，樓高24層，第2座亦同樣為24層。設有646伙，其中開放式佔69伙，佔全盤11%，1房戶設485伙，佔全盤75%，2房戶設92伙，佔全盤14%。<br />\n<br />\n另外，[img]項目實用面積最細為1A座6樓G室，實用面積只有179方呎，連33方呎平台[/img]，採開放式間隔，料為油塘區最細新盤。至於最大為2座5樓A室，實用面積574方呎，連354方呎花園，2房間隔。項目會所實用面積10,477方呎，住宅停車位只有61個，而公眾停車位則多達237個。預計關鍵日期為2019年9月30日，樓花期長不足一年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n印象中好似四球入場費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944a34be65951f4e92c4fbca80e0b35e50cbcdc8","tid":847600,"uid":104714,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:47:34.000Z","msg":"等冇人買"},{"pid":"dc05d56f9d222fb3bad0fbbf4cb7eab3fc749b42","tid":847600,"uid":135957,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:53:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"702a0b7a6fe243cbac4b120757cf6906befa03f4","tid":847600,"uid":144626,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:55:42.000Z","msg":"跟住港豬又排隊買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea4e3b1b8948afd0a73696e4e71d77238f91cad","tid":847600,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>印象中好似四球入場費</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\